description: Fortinova Fastigheter AB engages in the acquisition, development and management of properties. The company is headquartered in Varberg, Hallands and currently employs 22 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2020-11-19. The firm acquires, develops and manages residential properties in growth locations in western Sweden.
naicsNationalIndustry: Lessors of Residential Buildings and Dwellings
